             confirmed that of the two prisoners confession.</p>
               <p>Lankstone's Defence.</p>
               <p>My house-keeper gleaned the wheat, that the flour was made of in harvest.</p>
               <p>Smith's Defence.</p>
               <p>I am very innocent of it, they found nothing in the world upon me.</p>
               <p>Both <rs id="t17620114-14-verdict75" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17620114-14-verdict75" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
